\nthe membrane conductivity has to be relatively high, approximately one tenth of\nthe conductivity of the external aqueous medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Nov 2006 13:30:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Feb 2007 10:16:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
