ng the universal SUSY mass scale Lambda from the direct\nSUSY particle searches: Lambda > 40, 27, 21, 17, 15 TeV/c^2 for messenger\nindices N=1, 2, 3, 4, 5 respectively, for all NLSP lifetimes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 5 Nov 2006 23:07:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-20"}
